{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the amount of content on sexism in the PSHE national curriculum.",
        "additional_details": "As a student, I received minimal education on sexism in society. The only time where I properly learnt about it was  in A-Level History (when I was 16). I think this was too little, too late. I've witnessed the toxic masculinity that prevails within school  It is the lack of education on sexism (from a young age) which is a key reason for the gender inequality within society.",
        "background": "I ask the Secretary of State for Education to change the curriculum in order to increase education about sexism in society.",
